{"id":16,"date":"2017-07-07T19:08:51","date_gmt":"2017-07-07T19:08:51","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=16"},"modified":"2023-10-28T09:53:07","modified_gmt":"2023-10-28T09:53:07","slug":"faq","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/faq\/","title":{"rendered":"FAQ"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-10 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-3714\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-3714'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"Is it necessary to have my kitchen exhaust system cleaned?\"data-newtitle=\"Is it necessary to have my kitchen exhaust system cleaned?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >Is it necessary to have my kitchen exhaust system cleaned?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;  \"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]Yes. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.fda.gov\/media\/87140\/download\">The law<\/a> states that kitchen grease exhaust cleaning must be performed on a regular basis, and the Fire Marshal, Health Inspector and your insurance company will be closely monitoring your compliance. The law isn\u2019t set out to inconvenience you. Vent hood cleaning to remove kitchen grease prevents fire and improves air flow, leading to a safer and cleaner kitchen environment. As an added bonus, you can improve the life of your vent hoods and exhaust systems by engaging in regular cleaning and maintenance.[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-7854\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-7854'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"How often should I have my vent hoods cleaned?\"data-newtitle=\"How often should I have my vent hoods cleaned?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >How often should I have my vent hoods cleaned?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;  \"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]At Hood Builder, we recommend that incredibly busy kitchens engage in quarterly cleaning schedules, such as those operating 24-hours per day. For moderately busy kitchens, a thorough cleaning every six months should suffice. Low-volume kitchens can get away with annual vent hood cleanings, but for kitchens that primarily use wood or coal, monthly cleanings might be best.[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-4158\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-4158'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"Why can\u2019t I just rely on my employees to clean my vent hoods?\"data-newtitle=\"Why can\u2019t I just rely on my employees to clean my vent hoods?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >Why can\u2019t I just rely on my employees to clean my vent hoods?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;padding-top:0px;margin-top:0px;\"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]Cleaning vent hoods and the ventilation systems they\u2019re attached to is a tedious task that requires experience, training and specialized equipment. If you employ individuals who happen to be qualified and certified, that is an ideal scenario for passing vent hood inspections and getting the most efficiency and safety from your vent hood performance.<\/p>\n<p>On the other hand, if you don\u2019t employ anyone who is qualified and certified to clean kitchen ventilation systems, it pays to hire a professional team like Hood Builder to do the work for you.[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-8649\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-8649'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"When I hire Hood Builder to clean my kitchen, will I have to shut my business down?\"data-newtitle=\"When I hire Hood Builder to clean my kitchen, will I have to shut my business down?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >When I hire Hood Builder to clean my kitchen, will I have to shut my business down?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;  \"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]At Hood Builder, we work around your schedule. You tell us when to clean and we\u2019ll show up with tools in hand, ready to get the job done to your complete satisfaction.[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-8910\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-8910'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"Do you adhere to any standards when performing vent hood cleaning and maintenance?\"data-newtitle=\"Do you adhere to any standards when performing vent hood cleaning and maintenance?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >Do you adhere to any standards when performing vent hood cleaning and maintenance?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;  \"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]Yes. At Hood Builder, our technicians are trained and certified in advanced cleaning systems course work as mandated by the National Fire Protection Association. The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nfpa.org\/\">NFPA<\/a> is the authority on fire, electrical and building safety protocols. When you choose Hood Builder, you can be sure that your vent hood cleaning, kitchen equipment maintenance and fire suppression system installation will adhere to the stringent standards of the NFPA and all other related associations.[\/vc_column_text]<\/div><\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_section_layer ult-adjust-bottom-margin wps-faq\" >\r\n\t<div id=\"uvc-exp-wrap-4070\"   data-ultimate-target='#uvc-exp-wrap-4070'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"desktop:18px;\",\"line-height\":\"desktop:20px;\"}'  class=\"ult_exp_section  ult-responsive \" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#dbdbdb;font-family:Montserrat;font-weight:500; padding-bottom:0px;\" data-textcolor=\"#333333\"data-texthover=\"#333333\"data-icncolor=\"#a9a790\"data-ihover=\"#a9a790\"data-height=\"0\"data-cntbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-cnthvrbg=\"#e5e5e5\"data-headerbg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-headerhover=\"#e5e5e5\"data-title=\"How much do you charge for vent hood cleaning in Denver?\"data-newtitle=\"How much do you charge for vent hood cleaning in Denver?\"data-icon=\"Defaults-plus-square-o\"data-newicon=\"Defaults-minus-square-o\"data-activeicon=\"#a9a790\"data-effect=\"slideToggle\"data-override=\"0\"data-activetitle=\"#333333\"data-activebg=\"#dbdbdb\"data-img=\"\"data-newimg=\"\"><div  class=\"ult_exp_section-main \">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ult_expheader\" align=\"center\" >How much do you charge for vent hood cleaning in Denver?\r\n\t\t\t\t\t <\/div>\t<div class=\"ult-just-icon-wrapper ult_exp_icon\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-icon \" style=\"text-align:center;margin-right:10px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<span class=\"aio-icon  none  ult_expsection_icon \"  style=\"color:#a9a790;font-size:20px;display:inline-block;\">\n\t<i class=\"Defaults-plus-square-o ult_ex_icon\"  ><\/i>\n<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div><div class=\"ult_exp_content \" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;  \"><div class=\"ult_ecpsub_cont\" style=\" \" >[vc_column_text]We wish we could tell you a definite figure to make the process easier to figure for your budget, but unfortunately there are several factors to consider. When determine how much to quote for a vent hood cleaning project, we take into consideration the type of system you have and the volume of work involved.<\/p>\n<p>However, we also guarantee that we can beat our competitors\u2019 prices, and offer special rates to our long-term clients. We don\u2019t want you to just use Hood Builder once. We want to return again and again to keep your vent hoods sparkling clean, your kitchen air clean, and your personnel safe from fire.<\/p>\n